    dc:description "Figure 137. Solanum pygmaeum A habit B flowering branch C flower D calyx E dissected calyx, adaxial surface F dissected flower G stamen, dorsal view H stamen, ventral view I gynoecium J fruit K seed (A-K Bernardello & DiFulvio 476). Illustration by L. Ribulgo. Previously published in Barboza et al. (2013: 256) and Saerkinen et al. (2018: 130)." ;
